snippet.title: Tom Hanks Reveals His Favourite Movie Of His Career
snippet.description:
With over 90 acting credits and two Academy Awards to his name, Tom Hanks has been a part of some memorable movies over the course of his career, but now the actor is revealing which of his films is his favourites. Spoiler alert: It's not "Forrest Gump".

#TomHanks
